# CVE suppressions for northwind-policy-hub
#
# Add CVEs here only when:
#   1. The fix is not yet available in the base image, AND
#   2. The vulnerability is not exploitable in this app's context
#
# Each entry must include a comment explaining why it is suppressed.

# ── npm-internal bundled dependencies ────────────────────────────────────────
# These CVEs are in /usr/local/lib/node_modules/npm/ — npm's own bundled
# packages that ship with node:20-alpine. They are NOT in our application's
# dependencies. npm is a build/install tool and is not used at runtime, so
# these vulnerabilities are not exploitable in production. The fix requires a
# newer Node.js LTS release that bundles an updated npm version.

# cross-spawn 7.0.3 (npm bundled dep) — ReDoS
CVE-2024-21538

# glob 10.4.2 (npm bundled dep)
CVE-2025-64756

# minimatch (npm bundled dep) — ReDoS variants
CVE-2026-26996
CVE-2026-27903
CVE-2026-27904

# sigstore 2.3.1 (npm bundled dep)
CVE-2026-48815

# tar 6.2.1 (npm bundled dep) — path traversal / symlink variants
CVE-2026-23745
CVE-2026-23950
CVE-2026-24842
CVE-2026-26960
